## Custom Commands

Create workflows as markdown files:

- Project: `.claude/commands/*.md`
- Personal: `~/.claude/commands/*.md`

Execute with `/project:command-name` or `/user:command-name`.

Files in subdirectories get namespaced: `.claude/frontend/component.md` becomes `/frontend:component`.

Commands support `$ARGUMENTS` for all args, or `$1`, `$2` for positional parameters.
